query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	iamGetUsers (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		code
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		username
		password
		rememberToken
		data
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	iamFindUser (query: $query)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		code
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		username
		password
		rememberToken
		data
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	iamFindUserById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		code
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		username
		password
		rememberToken
		data
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

{

		id
		accountId
		name
		surname
		code
		avatar
		mobile
		langId
		username
		password
		rememberToken
		data
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
